  <div class="page">
    <p>We created a testbed to analyze the security of aircraft</p>
    <p>Analyzing the security of aircraft systems</p>
    <p>What happens if an attacker compromises an airplanes electronics? - Can it make the airplane operate in an unsafe manner?</p>
    <p>- Can it make the pilots think an unsafe condition is safe?</p>
    <p>We need to attack a genuine airplane to answer these questions - Attacks in simulation or theory are difficult to believe</p>
    <p>- Testing on an airplane is impractical</p>
  </div>
