  <div class="page">
    <p>Inputs</p>
    <p>Airborne Data Loader (ADL)</p>
    <p>Connects to all other computers</p>
    <p>Loads software/data updates</p>
    <p>Security: Malicious software</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>Inputs</p>
    <p>VHF Data Radio (VDR)</p>
    <p>For ACARS: Air-ground text communication</p>
    <p>Converts radiotext</p>
    <p>Security: Entry point, accepts all messages</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>Inputs</p>
    <p>Multifunction control and display unit (MCDU)</p>
    <p>Interface between pilots and computers</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>Inputs</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>The CMU is the heart</p>
    <p>Communications Management Unit (CMU)</p>
    <p>Processes all ACARS messages from VDR</p>
    <p>Forwards messages to other devices</p>
    <p>Security: Parses untrusted input, well-connected</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>The CMU is the heart</p>
