    <p>More computers</p>
    <p>Flight Management Computer (FMC)</p>
    <p>Navigates, calculates performance parameters</p>
    <p>Sometimes controls autopilot</p>
    <p>Receives ACARS messages through CMU</p>
    <p>Security: Directly influences flight</p>
